snippet.title: SkateNationXL - Official Game Announcement Trailer | Releasing Soon
snippet.description:
Introducing #SkateNationXL, the incredible upcoming skateboard arcade game!

Get ready to immerse yourself in a realistic skateboarding adventure, exploring vast skateparks, urban landscapes, and iconic real-world spots. With user-friendly controls, an advanced trick system, and an inspiring progression system, you’ll experience a rewarding sense of accomplishment and a fresh face of the ultimate skateboarding experience.

SkateNationXL is now available to Wishlist on PlayStation, Steam and Epic Games Store.

Wishlist Now: 
Steam: https://www.skatenationxl.com/steam
Epic Games: https://www.skatenationxl.com/epic-games
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011353
